Wiring Guide
OLED (I2C)
OLED Pin	ESP32 Pin
SDA	GPIO 21
SCL	GPIO 22
VCC	3.3V
GND	GND
HC-SR04
HC-SR04 Pin	ESP32 Pin
VCC	5V
Trig	GPIO 12
Echo	GPIO 13
GND	GND
Line Sensors (Example for 3x TCRT5000)
Left: GPIO 32

Middle: GPIO 35

Right: GPIO 34

L298N Motor Driver
IN1 → GPIO 25

IN2 → GPIO 26

IN3 → GPIO 27

IN4 → GPIO 14
